                            <comment id="13280519" author="yseeley@gmail.com" created="Mon, 21 May 2012 21:30:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Here&apos;s a draft patch that doesn&apos;t quite work yet.  The direction I&apos;m going is to add flags to the tlog entries when adding buffered entries.  On startup, we look at (and keep track of) the latest entry.  If the flag is set, then we don&apos;t try peersync when we are recovering.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
